<li id="cite_note-22"><b><a href="#cite_ref-22" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.sidis.net/Calendar.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.sidis.net/Calendar.htm" rel="nofollow">Perpetual Calendar</a></li>
