<li id="cite_note-24"><b><a href="#cite_ref-24" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFKett.2C_Joseph_F.1978">Kett, Joseph F. (1978). "Curing the Disease of Precocity". <i>The <a href="/wiki/American_Journal_of_Sociology" title="American Journal of Sociology">American Journal of Sociology</a></i> <b>84 (suppl.)</b>: S183–S211.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Curing+the+Disease+of+Precocity&amp;rft.jtitle=The+%5B%5BAmerican+Journal+of+Sociology%5D%5D&amp;rft.aulast=Kett%2C+Joseph+F.&amp;rft.au=Kett%2C+Joseph+F.&amp;rft.date=1978&amp;rft.volume=84+%28suppl.%29&amp;rft.pages=S183%E2%80%93S211&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:William_James_Sidis"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
